  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class RelatedEntitiesHistoricalFindRequest
extends RelatedEntitiesFindRequest
    RelatedEntitiesHistoricalFindRequest provides an extension to the search parameters to include the point in time that the request should be based on. This extension is used since historical queries are optional support.
